Subject_Line: This week, enjoy savoury bites, on us
Preheader: Sky VIP - it's a thank you from us
Main_Headline: Check out your top rewards this week from Sky VIP
Hero_Image_Alt_Text: The Spongebob Movie: Sponge Out of Water film poster
Hero_Copy: Kick off the new year with a super-awesome movie night in, on us. Dim the lights, grab your snacks and download The Spongebob Movie: Sponge Out of Water from Sky Store. It's all yours to keep, for free. It's our way of saying thank you.
Hero_CTA_Copy: Claim now in the My Sky app
Sports_3_Image_Alt_Text: The Athletic app on a phone screen
Sports_Copy: This is your last chance to get 15% off Target Darts equipment. Or, enter to win tickets to a Sky Bet Championship home fixture of your choice. Plus, claim 1 year of access to The Athletic and score personalised coverage of your favourite sports, on us.
Sports_CTA_Copy: Find out more in the My Sky app
Rewards_on_Repeat_Heading: Enjoy your weekly treat, on us
Rewards_on_Repeat_Image_Alt_Text: A box of Sainsbury's Taste The Difference savoury bites
Rewards_on_Repeat_Copy: This week, get cosy on the sofa and enjoy a box of Sainsbury's Taste The Difference savoury bites. Head to Rewards on Repeat in the My Sky app to claim your coupon.*
Rewards_on_Repeat_CTA_Copy: Claim now in the My Sky app
Experience_2_Image_Alt_Text: A poster showcasing a selection of Merlin attractions
Experience_Copy: Sing, learn, and play with JJ and friends when you enter to win one of 15 Cocomelon toy bundles for your little ones. Enter to win tickets to a Merlin attraction of your choice in London, including Madame Tussauds and the London Eye. Or, enter for your chance to win tickets to a preview screening of Send Help, in cinemas 6 February.
Experience_CTA_Copy: Enter now in the My Sky app
Everyday_Savings_Copy: This is your last chance to grab some amazing discounts before they refresh for January. Get your 1st month of dry dog food for free (+£2 delivery) from Tails.com. Find this and many more discounts in Everyday Savings in the VIP section of the My Sky app.
Everyday_Savings_CTA_Copy: Claim now in the My Sky app
Signoff_Copy: Make everyday a little better. It's a thank you from us.
